Name: Merry Christmas
Description:
Our best-selling Merry Christmas bouquet is the perfect way to make their day extraordinary this holiday season! This delightful floral arrangement features the timeless charm of beautiful red Rhodos roses paired with vibrant oriental lilies, finished off beautifully with red hypericum berries, fresh green foliage and a decorative Merry Christmas pick. Handcrafted by our skilled florists with meticulous attention to detail, this exquisite bouquet truly captivates the charm of the Christmas season! 

Whether you're looking for a meaningful present for a loved one or seeking to adorn your home with festive decor, this extraordinary bouquet will add a festive and fragrant touch to any space. Why not include a personalised card to send your warm wishes this festive season?
